high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn left to face the sink
Pick up the bowl and spoon from behind the sink
Turn around and take a step then turn left and go the fridge then turn right to face the fridge
Put the bowl and spoon in the fridge to chill then take the bowl and spoon out of the fridge
Turn left and head to the counter that is to the right of the stove
Put the bowl and spoon on the back of the counter, to the right of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl and spoon to the left of the coffee maker that is at the back of the counter

high_descs: Go to the sink in front of you.
Pick up the bowl on the counter, behind the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go toward the door, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge and chill it, then take the bowl out.
Turn left and go straight ahead to the counter.
Place the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Take a small step to your right.
Pick up the blue bowl that's in front of you above the sink.
Move to your right until you're facing the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn let and walk to the counter.
Put the bowl to the left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the counter.
